rticular near\nthe centers of the leading and trailing hemispheres, while the mid-latitudes\n(~30-60 degrees) are generally colder than predicted; these trends are\nsuggestive of an exogenic origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2021 22:04:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Jun 2021 16:44:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-08"}
