/K$. As its result, we can\nshow that there exists no equifocal submanifold with non-flat section in some\nirreducible simply connected symmetric spaces of compact type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 07:23:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 May 2021 04:55:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-05"}
