urement to amount to 150 meV. By adding the\nexcitonic binding energy of 0.2 eV obtained theoretically to the experimental\noptical absorption onset, we determine the fundamental band gap at room\ntemperature to be 4.55 eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 10:09:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
